{"id": 31760, "title": "Tsuru Shitae Waka Kan", "synopsis": "Spans 13 meters 53 cm long picture scroll painting by Sotatsu Tawaraya, \"Tsuru shitae waka kan (Anthology with Cranes)\" (17th Century) is a unique painting to evoke the moving image.\nYamamura try to decipher this \"Anthology with Cranes\" and the intent of Sotatsu Tawaraya, finished in experimental work and interpret it as animation.\n\n(Source: Yamamura Animation)"}